title: namami vijayaam
sahitya:
namAmi vijayAm phaNidhara jAyAm kumAra satpura nilayAm abhayAm

anupallavi

 umAm amEyAm sujana vidhEyAm shamAdi guNayuta munigaNa gEyAm

caraNam

 gAna kalAbhiratAm shrI lalitAm dInadayA bharitAm shubha caritAm 
dAnava vimatAm nirjara vinutAm kAnana tulasI saurabha niratAm
